divs: Sighting DetailsStandig out front having a cigarette with wife, sav 5 bojects come into view with no sound, they were in formation pattern. Tried to capture with cell phone cam ,and phone would not work. After they were gone phone worked and battery said it was deas.........Phone had been charging all day and normally works flawlessly. I use my cam and phone daily. Called 911 and made a report. There is an airport with in several miles and these were NOT AIRPLANES.
Summary: Saw 5 objects come into view in formation pattern, then disappear. Camera on phone wouldnt work and then battery displayed dead ...It was charging all day , and my phone always works!
